==== Design

    - *Type:* Secondary analysis of existing datasets
    - *Key datasets:* Any ME/CFS cohort with HRV, GI symptom, and microbiome data (e.g., Giloteaux et al.\ Cornell cohort @Giloteaux2016)
    - *Analysis:* Correlate HRV with GI symptom severity, butyrate-producer abundance, and fatigue scores; test whether HRV clusters identify a distinct subgroup
    - *Timeline:* 3–6 months
    - *Cost:* Low (secondary analysis, no new data collection)
